Summary: white circles in sky that disappeared and would appear back
divs: Sighting DetailsLast night I was outside in my yard when I looked up to the sky and noticed 3 white circle object forming a triangle and then a row. I don't know what the white circles where but I'm sure it was not a airplane or helicopter. As I was looking at the objects moving around I received a call from my husband who was looking at them too! I couldn't believe what I was looking at. As we were on the phone two of them dissapeared and before I could get my phone ready to video record it the 3rd object dissapeared too!
